milestones.description: Graham Gooch has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (3) in ODIs for ENG, going past Tony Greig's 2
England's 10-run win against New Zealand is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 14-run win against Pakistan
